        <updateDate>2019-09-05T15:47:51Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Help Students Vote Act</strong></p> <p>This bill addresses voter registration&nbsp;of students who attend&nbsp;institutions of higher education (IHEs) that participate in federal student aid programs, including by (1) requiring IHEs to make a good faith effort to distribute voter registration forms to each of their students at least twice a year, (2) authorizing grants to IHEs that greatly exceed the requirements governing the distribution of voter registration forms, and (3) allowing civil actions against IHEs that violate the requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
